      • CompoundFloatDataset

        public CompoundFloatDataset(int itemSize,
                            boolean repeat,
                            Dataset dataset)
        Cast a dataset to this compound type. If repeat is set, the first element of each item in the given dataset is repeated across all elements of an item. Otherwise, each item comprises a truncated or zero-padded copy of elements from the given dataset.
        Parameters:
        itemSize -
        repeat - repeat first element
        dataset -
